7. IOGP does not warrant that the GIGS Software will meet the full requirements of any particular testing framework and does not guarantee that the GIGS Test Series and GIGS Test Dataset will capture all facets of geodetic and geospatial integrity within a digital application. The completion of a GIGS Evaluation does not in any way therefore deem a digital application to be of a certain quality.

